@startuml client_init_and_failover_sd
title Object Client: SD, URMA, and failover

actor Client
participant "ObjectClientImpl" as OCI
participant "ServiceDiscovery" as SD
participant "EtcdStore" as Etcd
participant "ClientWorker\nRemoteApi" as CWA
participant "UrmaManager\nprocess-local" as UM
participant "Worker" as W

== Construct and SD inject ==
Client -> OCI: ConnectOptions with serviceDiscovery_
note right of OCI
  serviceDiscovery_ from ConnectOptions
  for Init and failover
end note

== A First connect with SD ==
Client -> OCI: Init
OCI -> SD: Init
SD -> Etcd: CreateTable
OCI -> SD: SelectWorker
SD -> Etcd: ObtainWorkers GetAll
Etcd --> SD: key value list
SD --> OCI: pick by affinity
alt same node and remote
  OCI -> OCI: InitPreferredRemoteFallback
  OCI -> W: InitClientWorkerConnectAt
else different path
  OCI -> OCI: set ipAddress_
  OCI -> W: InitClientWorkerConnect
end
W --> OCI: RegisterClient
OCI -> CWA: holds worker RPC session\nand heartbeat
OCI -> CWA: TryFastTransportAfterHeartbeat
CWA -> CWA: FastTransportHandshake
CWA -> CWA: InitializeFastTransportManager
opt if USE_URMA and Urma enabled
  CWA -> UM: local URMA init / warmup
  CWA -> CWA: AsyncFirstUrmaHandshake
  CWA -> W: TryUrmaHandshake (exchange / JFR)
  W --> CWA: ok or error
  alt handshake fails
    CWA -> CWA: FLAGS_enable_urma=false\nfallback TCP
    CWA -> CWA: optional ScheduleUrmaHandshakeRetry
  end
end
note right of CWA
  first URMA can finish after heartbeat starts
  version + stopUrmaHandshakeRetry_ avoid stale retry
  after new Worker
end note

== B Failover switch ==
Client -> OCI: trigger
OCI -> OCI: SwitchToStandbyWorkerImpl
OCI -> OCI: GetStandbyWorkersForSwitch
OCI -> SD: GetAllWorkers
SD -> Etcd: GetAll cluster
Etcd --> SD: KeepAlive values
SD --> OCI: partition filter self
note right of OCI
  TrySwitchToCandidateList
  Po2 may reorder
  load in KV can lag behind URMA READY
end note
OCI -> CWA: Disconnect (RPC if session up)
CWA -> W: Disconnect
W -> W: RemoveClient\n+ URMA / UB release on W
CWA -> CWA: dtor: stopUrmaHandshakeRetry_\nfd recv stop, reset handshake pools
OCI -> W: TrySwitchToStandbyWorker\nnew Init, Register on Standby
W --> OCI: RegisterClient Listen
OCI -> CWA: new ClientWorker instance
OCI -> CWA: TryFastTransportAfterHeartbeat
CWA -> UM: may reuse process UrmaManager
CWA -> W: URMA path as in A
OCI -> OCI: CommitStandbySwitch

@enduml
